{
  "stem": "9665.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Melitta had a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A fellow which I made it for, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Notovic, ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Klinge, ?] and my brother-in-law had visas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We all were put straight into prison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was an old castle, which they took us down that castle, which is still today a prison, but I-- I can't remember the name of--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was two weeks before we left for Spain, all of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three weeks before we left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That must have been in September, beginning of September.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they released Melitta immediately, within 12 hours, because I told them she's not well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They still had respect for women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[COUGHS] The other ones were released, including my brother-in-law, because he was worried about his hat, because he bought himself a new hat to travel to Spain and he was an Englishman.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he was-- and he put that on paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We still laughed about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were released.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the man from Vichy came and he was from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he interviewed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He spoke-- [NON-ENGLISH] was a province, which was before the First World War, German, and after the First World War, it was France.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after with the-- during the Hitler time, even before they invaded Holland, Belgium, and France, they took [NON-ENGLISH] back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He spoke German and French, this man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He interviewed me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in the beginning, he was very pleasant to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, you made these [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I went to a coffee shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And somebody said he can get me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He knows somebody in the prefecture, he can get it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But the only place where you can get a [NON-ENGLISH] was the prefecture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You made it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then I can't tell you-- the interrogation if this lasted 10 hours, 12 hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
